-- Flint Hills Released Benzene at Port Arthur Facility, NRC Says
-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 2012-03-27T07:31:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/flint-hills-released-benzene-at-port-arthur-facility-nrc-says.html
Flint Hills Resources LLC released
benzene and butadiene yesterday from its chemical plant in  Port
Arthur ,  Texas , according to a  filing  with the National Response
Center.  The emission occurred at 7:59 a.m. local time and the cause
was not immediately known, according to the filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
